<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RTI Application</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 150px;
        }
        .field-value {
            display: inline-block;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            min-width: 300px;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .content-box {
            border: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            min-height: 100px;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .date-place {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">APPLICATION UNDER RIGHT TO INFORMATION ACT, 2005</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <span class="field-label">To:</span>
        <span class="field-value">{{ public_information_officer or "The Public Information Officer" }}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <span class="field-label">Department:</span>
        <span class="field-value">{{ department or "[Department Name]" }}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <span class="field-label">Office Address:</span>
        <span class="field-value">{{ office_address or "[Office Address]" }}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>Subject: Application for information under Right to Information Act, 2005</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <p>Sir/Madam,</p>
        <p>I, <strong>{{ applicant_name or "[Your Full Name]" }}</strong>, a citizen of India, hereby request the following information under the Right to Information Act, 2005:</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-box">
        <strong>Information Requested:</strong><br>
        {{ information_requested or "[Describe the specific information you are seeking. Be as detailed and specific as possible.]" }}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>Purpose of Information:</strong><br>
        {{ purpose or "[State the purpose for which you need this information]" }}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>Period of Information:</strong><br>
        From: {{ period_from or "[Start Date]" }} To: {{ period_to or "[End Date]" }}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>Mode of receiving information:</strong><br>
        ☐ Inspection of records<br>
        ☐ Certified copies<br>
        ☐ Email: {{ email or "[Your Email]" }}<br>
        ☐ Post to address mentioned below
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>Applicant Details:</strong><br>
        Name: {{ applicant_name or "[Your Full Name]" }}<br>
        Address: {{ applicant_address or "[Your Complete Address]" }}<br>
        Phone: {{ phone or "[Your Phone Number]" }}<br>
        Email: {{ email or "[Your Email Address]" }}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <p>I am enclosing herewith an application fee of Rs. {{ application_fee or "10" }}/- (Rupees {{ application_fee_words or "Ten" }} only) in the form of {{ fee_mode or "demand draft/cash" }}.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <p>If the information sought is not available with your office, kindly transfer this application to the concerned office under intimation to me.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <p>I request you to provide the information within the stipulated time limit of 30 days as prescribed under the RTI Act, 2005.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="date-place">
        <div>
            <strong>Place:</strong> {{ place or "[Place]" }}<br>
            <strong>Date:</strong> {{ current_date }}
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div>Signature of Applicant</div>
            <div>{{ applicant_name or "[Your Name]" }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section" style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <strong>Enclosures:</strong><br>
        1. Application fee of Rs. {{ application_fee or "10" }}/-<br>
        2. Copy of identity proof (if required)
    </div>
</body>
</html>
